      "text": "それは、ペーパードライバーと言うのでは……？\n無理して運転しなくてもいいって言ったじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Isn't that what you call a \"paper driver\"…?\nI told you that you didn't have to drive if it was too much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 191.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
