      "text": "別に。……むしろ、本当にこの世に幽霊がいるのなら\n会いたい人に、会わせてほしいものですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not really. …In fact‚ if ghosts really exist in this world‚\nI'd want them to let me see the person I miss.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 229.6666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
