      "text": "……ともかく、俺もなるべく練習に付き合いますから\n場所と時間を変えましょう、近隣にも迷惑ですし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Anyway‚ I'll help you with your practice as much as I can.\nLet's change the time and place. It's a nuisance to the neighbors.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 235.8000015259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_02-mhk015.m4a",
      "text": "貴方が勝手についてくる分にはご勝手に\n……どうせ、嫌だと言っても聞かないでしょうし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I won't stop you if you insist on coming along.\n…Since you wouldn't listen even if I said no anyway.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 243.9333348592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
